comments.body: I've been looking forward to a period where a thread for female football will be created tho. Ive been following the game and it seems so far the hosts Uganda are sure candidates to winning this tournament. Set to play against Ethiopia, I feel they will encounter a little challenge because the Ethiopia women have shown that they too can hold their own. If I am to place a bet on this match, it will be a GG and ov 2.5.
